{
  "stem": "13623.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "People just ran as fast as they could across.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- the old public school, before they assembled us over there, was used by-- by the army as stables for their horses.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When we all had to run into the-- to the-- to that stable, to that public school that was turned into the stable, there was all kinds of horse manure and all kinds of dirt on the floor.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But you just had to run in and do what you're told.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Or, you knew what the consequence was-- a stick on your back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father and I were together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother and the rest of the family, because they were all smaller, younger than I was at the time, they were at home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was hardly enough time to-- to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we always hoped that this is not the last time we're going to see each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- it was more of a goodbye, like, I'm going to see you soon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That day that we got all assembled in that-- that-- that public school that turned into stables later on, the men were all-- at night, when we were all finally assembled, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a Hungarian officer [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] came up and made us all line up like soldiers, like the army would line up.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He counted-- he counted all of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's berating us, telling us, you dirty Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The war is all your fault.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We're in a war now that you-- you brought up on us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I'm going to make sure that you're going to stay here all night on your feet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you're not going to be able to go in, back into the building.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
